SoundClassEffects: Array of changes to be applied to groups.
InitialDelay: Initial delay in seconds before the mix is applied.
FadeInTime: Time taken in seconds for the mix to fade in.
Duration: Duration of mix, negative means it will be applied until another mix is set.
FadeOutTime: Time taken in seconds for the mix to fade out.
bApplyEQ: Whether to apply the EQ effect
